什么是大势？就是降低房地产、金融、教育、互联网等的利润和垄断，以及由此引发的过去长期对民生和实体经济的挤压和成本，大力发展制造业、硬科技、实体经济、新能源、新基建、资本市场等。百年未遇之大变局，也是百年未有之大机遇。看清这一大趋势，至关重要。每个企业每个人最终都是时代的产物。 以上，是经济学家任泽平博士，8月9日分享的最新观点。 任泽平博士认为，当下政策正在往重视公平、兼顾效率方向调整，主要是因为收入分配的差距，以及中国面临的K型复苏。未来货币宽松的时间窗口正在打开。同时，他还谈到了对于房地产如何软着陆、三胎生育政策、规范学科培训、中美关系等问题的看法。 任泽平：中国生育主力人群是75-85后 不要指望90后00后生"},"attached_info":"ClUI7POxgdyjt9QmEAMaCDY4OTY4ODQxIO7k54gGMEc4xQVAFHIJNDgwMDkyNzMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"287 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-16a12ce88246943baf285fd7546056f7_1440w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1629121175.6695557","card_id":"Q_479934492","target":{"id":479934492,"title":"为什么金庸的小说反复被翻拍成电视剧，但电视剧的口碑一次比一次差？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/479934492","type":"question","created":1629024497,"answer_count":161,"follower_count":378,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2102,4016,4513,5510,377089],"comment_count":15,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I7POxgdyjt9QmEAMaCDY4OTMzNDk0IPHh44gGMA84+gJAFXIJNDc5OTM0NDkyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"265 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-d0de3399c2fd9b0114bc0ae6b0c9ef96_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1629121175.670051","card_id":"Q_478914926","target":{"id":478914926,"title":"《扫黑风暴》有哪些细节让人细思恐极？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/478914926","type":"question","created":1628651385,"answer_count":44,"follower_count":305,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2102,5510,666197],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info"